---
title: Double Tandoori Chicken Drumsticks & Coconut Rice with Kachumber-Style Salad & Crushed Peanuts
description: When it comes to chicken, we’re always looking for two things: golden crackly skin and juicy, flavourful meat. Enter, these baked
chicken legs. They’re all that and then some—the “some” being a dry North Indian spice rub that really takes them above and
beyond. They’re served with fluffy rice, plus our twist on a kachumber salad. Ready to get a leg up on dinnertime?
